Toronto Generators (formerly Paga Technologies) has been installing and servicing standby generators since 2002. When the power goes out, a standby generator comes on automatically, restoring power to your home, business or cottage. We proudly supported our many clients through the December 2013 ice storm, and have expanded in order to continue providing exceptional service to our growing customer base.

We pride ourselves on our exceptional customer service, and our staff have the knowledge, experience and training to answer all of your questions. We would be happy to provide you with a site visit and written quote free of charge, so please call us today! Our specialty is Generator Installation and Service!

Amp Champ Inc. is a family owned electrical contracting business based in beautiful Collingwood.  We are proud to serve the greater Georgian Bay area; repairing and installing anything electrical in your home.

We at Amp Champ promise to find solution for any of your electrical problems.   
It is one of our goals to be known for our honesty and best in customer service in the Georgian Bay Area.

Our Amp Champ electricians strive to be environmentally friendly by installing it right the first time, recycling and ensuring environmentally cleaner options.   
To know that you, your family and your neighbourhood are safe because your home is electrically safe, gives us huge satisfaction and peace of mind. We are proud partners in building healthy, strong and SAFE communities.
